---
title: Crispy Shallot Sausage Croquettes with Mash, Gravy and Sautéed Brussels Sprouts
description: Big texture and bold taste are on the menu tonight! Sausage patties are breaded with crushed crispy shallot coating, then baked to achieve a craveable crunch. Tender-crisp veggies and velvety gravy round out the plate.
